title: "PR #200 review: batch validate prune-missing auto-fix removals"
description: "Gemini review on PR #200 found validate --auto-fix prune-missing applies each stale file/doc removal separately, causing repeated locks, writes, and hooks for multiple stale links on the same item. Batch prune removals by item and link kind."
