resolution: implemented
expected_result: validate --prune-missing auto-fix removes multiple stale files/docs for the same item with one files/docs mutation per link kind.
actual_result: Prune fixes are grouped by item and kind; the unit test verifies one runFiles and one runDocs removal call for multiple stale links while preserving per-fix output rows.
